{"tid":2152913,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"突發重要指示稱「粒粒皆辛苦」 恐遭美斷糧 習禁浪費食物","createTime":"2020-08-12T08:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T15:22:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":148,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"517ee9ff0718876f6ac2cd87e947c83c2581278b","tid":2152913,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T08:51:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200812/5F6TAI5N4COEEUR2N7XCZTOAAU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200812%2F5F6TAI5N4COEEUR2N7XCZTOAAU%2F&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWfxZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=53c68f2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200812%2F5F6TAI5N4COEEUR2N7XCZTOAAU%2F&h=737fe4f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200812/5F6TAI5N4COEEUR2N7XCZTOAAU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n突發重要指示稱「粒粒皆辛苦」<br />\n恐遭美斷糧 習禁浪費食物<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中國糧食問題令人擔心。中國國家主席習近平昨發出重要指示，稱要制止人民浪費食物的行為，形容現在餐飲浪費現象「觸目驚心、令人痛心」，稱對糧食安全始終要有危機意識，需要加強立法。學者指，這是因為中美紛爭可能會導致中國難以進口糧食，故現在要先作準備；消息人士稱，美國是中國糧食的供應國，習近平這次發出重要指示，是要「提防美國卡脖子」，也要提防特朗普突然出招，讓中美貿易出現問題。<br />\n<br />\n新華社昨報道，習近平發出重要指示，指餐飲浪費現象，觸目驚心、令人痛心，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MFLu-AUuYnG0PqaTzIl8BH9Ocmw=/640x519/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QP73JIGUDP4BWRNK3YCJ7I57II.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMFLu-AUuYnG0PqaTzIl8BH9Ocmw%3D%2F640x519%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQP73JIGUDP4BWRNK3YCJ7I57II.jpg&h=71c82612&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n習近平頻頻關注中國糧食問題，更發出重要指示要加強立法，制止浪費；圖為他早前巡視吉林農地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「提防美國卡脖子」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：浪費份量夠半億人吃一年<br />\n<br />\n消息人士表示，內地糧食大量依靠進口，美國是主要的出口國，這一次國家領導人作出重要指示，要求民眾不要浪費糧食主要。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n熟悉中國糧農問題的經濟學者胡星斗對本報表示，雖然中國目前沒有逼切的糧食問題，但也應該擔憂很有可能出現的糧食危機，。。。。。。。。。。。膨脹加劇，人民幣也會貶值。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n糧食「內循環」說易行難<br />\n<br />\n胡星斗指，這一年除了疫情，還出現洪災、蝗災等，甚至有虛報糧食的問題，聯合國也警告全球有可能出現饑荒，中國不能。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n近月習近平對國內糧食問題十分關心，上月下旬他曾到吉林考察玉米地，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n在兩會期間，習近平也指出，「對我們這樣一個有14億人口的大國來說，。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"02988f905b4d2755a07673ab18f04feaa9980300","tid":2152913,"uid":14103,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T08:56:14.000Z","msg":"你叫你班廢柴支那狗屙完尿要洗手都未得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf5e87fc48a28ccdbd35489f5810e17a2147d4d","tid":2152913,"uid":2429,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T08:58:57.000Z","msg":"食屎痾飯。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e908b763cb66e07e1e07a49b20217dc95e8e92e0","tid":2152913,"uid":35820,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:02:03.000Z","msg":"買咁多大豆 粟米都唔夠食？"},{"pid":"e76aa1782b6ec337eada9ecca1235ff9a9028e99","tid":2152913,"uid":293677,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:02:35.000Z","msg":"自己肚滿腸肥<br />\n但叫人食少D<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76fef96d374f2f90bf247ecef86eb05e00109ca6","tid":2152913,"uid":35820,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:03:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcS1PUbrTFckQdE9Mu71-zeDCgqIbuUk0ME3CA&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcS1PUbrTFckQdE9Mu71-zeDCgqIbuUk0ME3CA%26usqp%3DCAU&h=f889d791&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"952f6df6746ca20ef36fcdf2ce5a4c3ef94ae807","tid":2152913,"uid":253016,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:04:10.000Z","msg":"咪話撚左內循環<br />\n食完屙出黎再食番落肚再屙番出黎<br />\n一餐飯食三次 